{"tid":960210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"浴室天花有水漬水泡","createTime":"2018-12-29T08:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T16:24:54.000Z","uid":216521,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bfae4f88ab64a2211b535fa5419bac2ab1d977eb","tid":960210,"uid":216521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VszM3hW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVszM3hW.png&h=18e9f182&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzFo5wh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzFo5wh.png&h=f306df56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面兩張圖係岩岩發生時影既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxJqzpN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxJqzpN.png&h=df3a47fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfBSYRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfBSYRt.png&h=4f94e98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依兩張就今日影，時隔大約五，六日到<br />\n<br />\n發覺水泡大左多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問有冇巴打熟悉依類野可以解答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前情況: 已經通知左食環，但都知唔夠35%唔會受理<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但如果真係流水，甚至係咸水，驚會獨電同影響結構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6802a8978c9ab7facfc36b65b7dcd27b5644a9e","tid":960210,"uid":150378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"滲水你就有排受啦！"},{"pid":"f7ba0e44ca2673bd74b107cac2ceba9047a3fbb0","tid":960210,"uid":216521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"補充返 係咪都好大機會係上面水喉/去水位 滲水先會做左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eca905386761a629e19a76dc62cefd052c0fa8","tid":960210,"uid":186155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"